window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The plan was simple: Destroy the girl. Ruin her life. Make her and her mother leave.</p> <p>Only…she’s not as easy a target as I thought she’d be.</p> <p>She’s nothing but a pawn, a tool for my father to use against her mother.</p> <p>But pawns don’t fight back the way she does. They don’t violate my sanity the way she does.</p> <p>She put herself in the mouth of the beast.</p> <p>I wanted her out of the way, but now…I can’t let her go.</p> <p>This myth of Icarus retelling contains the following tropes and content warnings: college and mafia settings; stepbrother relationship; enemies-to-lovers; forbidden romance; mention of previous sexual assault, depictions of bullying, parental neglect/abuse, violence, murder, and human trafficking; depictions of consensual non-consent and pushing of boundaries. Discretion is advised.</p>"; 
